@startuml KointossDFDLevel0
!theme plain
scale 0.9
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor lightblue
  BorderColor darkblue
  FontSize 11
}
skinparam entity {
  BackgroundColor lightgreen
  BorderColor darkgreen
  FontSize 10
}
skinparam storage {
  BackgroundColor lightyellow
  BorderColor orange
  FontSize 10
}

title Kointoss - Data Flow Diagram (Level 0)
subtitle Context Diagram - Crypto Social Platform

' External Entities
entity "Guest User" as Guest
entity "Registered User" as User
entity "System Admin" as Admin
entity "CoinGecko API" as CoinGecko
entity "AWS Bedrock" as Bedrock

' Main System Process
rectangle "Kointoss\nCrypto Social Platform\n(Process 0)" as MainSystem

' Data Stores (External)
storage "AWS DynamoDB\n(User Data)" as UserDB
storage "AWS S3\n(Media Files)" as S3Storage

' Data Flows from External Entities to System
Guest --> MainSystem : Registration Request\nMarket Data Request\nContent View Request
User --> MainSystem : Login Credentials\nPost/Article Content\nPortfolio Data\nChat Messages\nProfile Updates
Admin --> MainSystem : Admin Commands\nContent Moderation\nUser Management
CoinGecko --> MainSystem : Real-time Crypto Prices\nMarket Statistics\nCoin Information
Bedrock --> MainSystem : AI Response Data\nMarket Analysis\nPersonalized Insights

' Data Flows from System to External Entities
MainSystem --> Guest : Market Data\nPublic Content\nRegistration Confirmation
MainSystem --> User : Personalized Feed\nPortfolio Analytics\nAI Insights\nNotifications\nSocial Updates
MainSystem --> Admin : System Analytics\nUser Reports\nContent Lists
MainSystem --> CoinGecko : API Requests\nData Sync Commands
MainSystem --> Bedrock : User Context\nMarket Queries\nPersonalization Data

' Data Flows between System and Data Stores
MainSystem <--> UserDB : User Profiles\nPosts & Comments\nPortfolio Data\nGamification Stats\nArticles & Interactions
MainSystem <--> S3Storage : Profile Pictures\nPost Images\nArticle Media\nBackup Files

' Positioning
Guest -[hidden]- User
User -[hidden]- Admin
CoinGecko -[hidden]- Bedrock

@enduml
